<plot>A look at the training methods of the San Francisco police department, showing how the young police officers are trained and equipped to fight crime. The course of intensive study covers, law, chemistry, ballistics, finger-print analysis and many other subjects. In the second half of this short, a real crime is reconstructed and the course of training is brought into application.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?423307</url></doc>
